extendedInfo.description: Choosing a DJ company for your next event can be a very difficult decision. Whether you are planning a Wedding, Quinces, Sweet Sixteen, Baby Shower, School or Corporate Event, DJ KLASSICK & COMPANY of Las Vegas, Nevada is the best choice. With many years of experience our DJ's and Emcee's will bring out the best in every event. Our professional and reliable staff has full knowledge of what works and what does not work on every type of event. Through music selection and personal interaction our DJ's and Emcee's motivate and entertain your guests, leaving them with lasting memories for years to come. Not all DJ's are alike. That is why at DJ KLASSICK & COMPANY we have a variety of DJ's to fit your style and needs. From the 1950's through today, our 60,000+ extensive music library has any and all songs for any event.So why should you hire DJ KLASSICK & COMPANY for your next event? Simply because we are the best at what we do. What is the secret to our success? We have professional, reliable, and creative DJ's and Emcee's who will cater to your style and wishes. The difference between our competition and us, we listen. We take in all of your wishes and combine them with our experience and you get the most fun possible in any one night. Our experienced staff will help plan your event from the beginning to the end.
